  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A first-person horror game set in a dark asylum where danger lurks around every corner.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382220/extras/26055386123d5f89b767236659a497ca.poster.avif?t=1751967854\" width=720 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382220/extras/26055386123d5f89b767236659a497ca.webm?t=1751967854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382220/extras/26055386123d5f89b767236659a497ca.mp4?t=1751967854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The doctor turned his patients into test subjects for ruthless experiments.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But one escaped. Hiding in the dark, hunting for revenge.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And she is here too… The ghost of the woman who died in the experiments.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Her screams still echo, her rage never fades.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Do your job, or die</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deliver experimental drugs, monitor patients, and prevent escapes. Overdosing means death.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382220/extras/f12291c7ac3fc6745bb20a3ec2142440.poster.avif?t=1751967854\" width=720 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382220/extras/f12291c7ac3fc6745bb20a3ec2142440.webm?t=1751967854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382220/extras/f12291c7ac3fc6745bb20a3ec2142440.mp4?t=1751967854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The killer is hunting you</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run, lock doors, hide. But you can’t hide forever.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382220/extras/a0ad8806300b8b0831aee69cc2840705.poster.avif?t=1751967854\" width=720 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382220/extras/a0ad8806300b8b0831aee69cc2840705.webm?t=1751967854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382220/extras/a0ad8806300b8b0831aee69cc2840705.mp4?t=1751967854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Send the recordings</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An unknown force demands the camera footage. If you refuse, you might be next.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Terror and desperation</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The patients rely on you. The doctor watches you. The killer hunts you. Can you survive until dawn?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A first-person horror game set in a dark asylum where danger lurks around every corner.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382220/extras/26055386123d5f89b767236659a497ca.poster.avif?t=1751967854\" width=720 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382220/extras/26055386123d5f89b767236659a497ca.webm?t=1751967854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382220/extras/26055386123d5f89b767236659a497ca.mp4?t=1751967854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The doctor turned his patients into test subjects for ruthless experiments.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But one escaped. Hiding in the dark, hunting for revenge.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And she is here too… The ghost of the woman who died in the experiments.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Her screams still echo, her rage never fades.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Do your job, or die</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deliver experimental drugs, monitor patients, and prevent escapes. Overdosing means death.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382220/extras/f12291c7ac3fc6745bb20a3ec2142440.poster.avif?t=1751967854\" width=720 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382220/extras/f12291c7ac3fc6745bb20a3ec2142440.webm?t=1751967854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382220/extras/f12291c7ac3fc6745bb20a3ec2142440.mp4?t=1751967854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The killer is hunting you</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run, lock doors, hide. But you can’t hide forever.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382220/extras/a0ad8806300b8b0831aee69cc2840705.poster.avif?t=1751967854\" width=720 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382220/extras/a0ad8806300b8b0831aee69cc2840705.webm?t=1751967854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382220/extras/a0ad8806300b8b0831aee69cc2840705.mp4?t=1751967854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Send the recordings</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An unknown force demands the camera footage. If you refuse, you might be next.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Terror and desperation</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The patients rely on you. The doctor watches you. The killer hunts you. Can you survive until dawn?</p>",
